    <node id="Маленький принц">
      <data key="d0">Маленький принц</data>
      <data key="d1">person</data>
      <data key="d2">Маленький принц is described as a character from Antoine de Saint-Exupéry’s novella “Le Petit Prince”. He is portrayed as an unnamed, young prince who reflects deeply on life and human relationships. The prince is curious about his surroundings, especially the giant baobabs on his home planet and he understands their significance in terms of growth and fragility. He tries to share these insights with others through drawings, warning about potential dangers associated with these massive trees.

The character is described as human, young, naive, melancholic, introspective, and a visitor from another planet. There are various perspectives on his behavior; he may feel embarrassed by the behavior of a proud person. Throughout the story, Mаленький принц reflects deeply about life, human relationships, often warning against hubris and the importance of empathy.

The nameless prince is involved in an adventure across various landscapes including deserts and mountains, seeking to find his way through these places. He seeks guidance on how to truly love and be loved in the world, as well as seeking wisdom and understanding about life.&lt;SEP&gt;Princess in a storybook, fictional&lt;SEP&gt;Author of the fairy tale "The Little Prince"&lt;SEP&gt;Fictional character from the story "The Little Prince"</data>
      <data key="d3">doc-265544bb40b451cd313707a2a4b33ff4-chunk-000&lt;SEP&gt;doc-6b2ba88f29d6d77fed85771bc5dc9981-chunk-000&lt;SEP&gt;doc-adc6c168dbb425d9ece24d5bc28b2fcc-chunk-000&lt;SEP&gt;doc-1b8b1d20aa2c3a367e6898ef909e1830-chunk-000&lt;SEP&gt;doc-7ff80b28ae61d87cbbd16fc2977b0881-chunk-000&lt;SEP&gt;doc-a4e544d8de8adf2c2d92737023d20063-chunk-000&lt;SEP&gt;doc-483c61454a03ee080cf5d72363c83c1b-chunk-000&lt;SEP&gt;doc-80bf0fd8d2ff27add315189775433556-chunk-000&lt;SEP&gt;doc-f22f66c8caa291e65e02b802daf878c8-chunk-000&lt;SEP&gt;doc-b26c7bacf26ef15a3a45c68b68f9b575-chunk-000&lt;SEP&gt;doc-2893ddee83e92a02b0b7d4a6d9224c42-chunk-001&lt;SEP&gt;doc-2893ddee83e92a02b0b7d4a6d9224c42-chunk-000&lt;SEP&gt;doc-182370cff63e636c1b45ff0038b36f2d-chunk-000&lt;SEP&gt;doc-63642680210ac7cc8853ae5971b0f48c-chunk-000&lt;SEP&gt;doc-63642680210ac7cc8853ae5971b0f48c-chunk-001&lt;SEP&gt;doc-7b9896410b77cc024d82f44dc965accf-chunk-000&lt;SEP&gt;doc-b2ddc1d164c8ac85ef4ad08ae708f127-chunk-000&lt;SEP&gt;doc-308d87903d261998c818bf0ed07e7067-chunk-000&lt;SEP&gt;doc-a5c45dda9bea440567dafe4c7b25cf01-chunk-000&lt;SEP&gt;doc-15468bcb7ce72586bfabdda9ece08444-chunk-000&lt;SEP&gt;doc-46fdf55d158045ca310db2834879aaf8-chunk-000&lt;SEP&gt;doc-46fdf55d158045ca310db2834879aaf8-chunk-001&lt;SEP&gt;doc-60dfb0ba6b57b6233511a50d47891826-chunk-000&lt;SEP&gt;doc-7a5f69411979c59a0575f42c23b45672-chunk-000&lt;SEP&gt;doc-928b0034ba3f97de26a0b4b164cee252-chunk-000&lt;SEP&gt;doc-c9977c09ad87bbd636c24b2597c3ed88-chunk-000</data>
