      <data key="d2">The prince offers a chance of helping but the drunkard refuses any explanation.&lt;SEP&gt;Маленький принц asks the drunkard a question about why he drinks to forget.&lt;SEP&gt;The prince feels sorry for the drunkard and wants to help him.</data>
