    <node id="роза">
      <data key="d0">роза</data>
      <data key="d1">naturalobject</data>
      <data key="d2">A rare flower that represents the heart of two individuals, symbolizing their strong bond and devotion to one another through their shared experiences and care&lt;SEP&gt;A rare flower that is considered valuable due to its special place in the hearts of two individuals, the Little Prince and his guardian fox&lt;SEP&gt;A rare flower that represents the heart of two individuals, symbolizing their strong bond and devotion to one another&lt;SEP&gt;A rare flower that represents a strong bond between two individuals, the Little Prince and his guardian fox&lt;SEP&gt;A precious flower given to the Little Prince as a companion and symbol of his love for him</data>
      <data key="d3">doc-46fdf55d158045ca310db2834879aaf8-chunk-001</data>
      <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
      <data key="d5">1782426968</data>
      <data key="d6" />
    </node>
    <node id="Лис">
      <data key="d0">Лис</data>
      <data key="d1">creature</data>
      <data key="d2">Лис can be interpreted as both a friendly mentor for the Little Prince and an organization of foxes who practice ancient rituals with local girls on Thursdays. The first description emphasizes intimate knowledge sharing about true love, while the second describes the Fox's role in introducing a young prince to concepts of love and human connection through mentoring. The third highlights the intimate knowledge shared between the Fox and the Little Prince, focusing on love rather than broader connections. One fourth instance mentions an organization of foxes engaging in ritual dancing with local girls. Another description portrays the Fox as merely friendly and helpful without any ritualistic or deeper connection details. Finally, one entry describes a hunting fox, indicating this might be a different entity or perhaps referring to another context not fully defined within the given descriptions.&lt;SEP&gt;Fox, mythical being fictional</data>
      <data key="d3">doc-46fdf55d158045ca310db2834879aaf8-chunk-000&lt;SEP&gt;doc-46fdf55d158045ca310db2834879aaf8-chunk-001&lt;SEP&gt;doc-7a5f69411979c59a0575f42c23b45672-chunk-000&lt;SEP&gt;doc-928b0034ba3f97de26a0b4b164cee252-chunk-000</data>
