      <data key="d7">13.0</data>
      <data key="d8">The relation describes various aspects and reactions towards a flower in the book "The Little Prince". The descriptions highlight tenderness, foolishness, respect, and sadness. There is also an observation of fragrance, curiosity about its origins, doubt, understanding, admiration, and anticipation for something extraordinary related to this flower.</data>
