    <edge source="Маленький принц" target="Лис">
      <data key="d7">25.0</data>
      <data key="d8">Лис, Маленький принц. The description list provides various aspects of this relation. Several descriptions focus on teaching and helping someone through important connections or relationships, sharing feelings and making others feel cared for, and learning life lessons from a close relationship. One description highlights understanding something deeply after receiving it from someone trusted. Another emphasizes sharing personal experiences with a person deemed very important in one's life. A few notes mention being held in high regard due to one’s role or qualities, as well as teaching or mentoring someone, specifically the young prince. Lastly, a description indicates engaging in conversation and speaking with the young prince. These descriptions collectively describe an educational, supportive, and intimate relationship between the Lys and a young prince, where lessons are shared and deep connections are fostered.&lt;SEP&gt;Providing advice on dealing with the lack of water and survival techniques.</data>
      <data key="d9">Appointed as guardian to,Learned from,Planned to help,Received guidance from,Received understanding from,Respected by,Taught by,Trained by,gave_advice_on_survival,talks_with</data>
      <data key="d10">doc-46fdf55d158045ca310db2834879aaf8-chunk-000&lt;SEP&gt;doc-46fdf55d158045ca310db2834879aaf8-chunk-001&lt;SEP&gt;doc-7a5f69411979c59a0575f42c23b45672-chunk-000</data>
