    <edge source="he" target="she">
      <data key="d7">21.0</data>
      <data key="d8">he: In this context, he appears to be cautious and protective, worried about the safety of someone (likely she) due to a snake. He brings joy to her by remembering past experiences together. There is also an element of anticipation as he promises something special for her.

she: The initial impression suggests she has mixed feelings. She doesn't fully understand him at times, needing clarification or explanation. Conversely, she wants his companionship and listens eagerly when he shares ideas with her, showing a desire to share experiences. However, there are moments where she feels scared or warned about potential dangers such as the snake.

There appears to be some overlapping between 'he' and 'she,' but overall distinct behaviors and situations have been identified for both entities within this relation "he, she."</data>
      <data key="d9">Arriving,Being amused,Carrying,Concerning,Desiring,Distancing,Fear,Friendship,Giving,Joy,Leaving,Listening,Other,Sharing,Surprised,Trying,Understanding,Warning,Window opening,Witnessing,Змея</data>
      <data key="d10">doc-676d5cefe7ff1a128d8fdfe77978f0fd-chunk-001</data>
      <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
      <data key="d12">1782427852</data>
      <data key="d13" />
    </edge>
